title: Brad Keselowski wins the pole for Chase race at Kansas Speedway
text: Brad Keselowski wins the pole for Chase race at Kansas Speedway Friday, 16 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) Team Penske's Brad Keselowski was fastest in qualifying for the Hollywood Casino 400 at Kansas Speedway, putting him on the pole for Sunday's second race in the Contender Round of the Chase for the Sprint Cup Team Penske driver Brad Keselowski will start Sunday's NASCAR Sprint Cup Chase race at Kansas Motor Speedway race from pole ahead of Carl Edwards Autosport 28 minutes ago - Sports Brad Keselowski leads contingent of Chase challengers to win pole for race at Kansas Speedway ABCNews.com 34 minutes ago - Front Page Take a look at the results from Friday's opening NASCAR Sprint Cup Series practice session for Sunday's Hollywood Casino 400 at Kansas Speedway.
